column5: I'll be staying at Lac Seul Lodge from June 28 - July 4. I know Pooch will be at the lodge that same week. Any other regular WC posters in the area during that week? If so, what sort of boat will you be in? If I see you I'll say hello.
I will be up on lac suel. Staying at my buddies parents house in hudson. Grey and red crestliner.
